name: MALLU REPUBLIC

reviews.review_text: I tried chicken fry , Appam and Parotta and would rate them around 3.5 /5 as many mallus recommended this place I had alot of expectations the flavour/ punch of spices was missing and my friends had some beef fry and beef masala they said it's good so you can give a try and there are very less veg options

Ordered through Swiggy for guests (bill att).
Will not deny. Taste is good.
however, the items received were wrong. moreover Item recived was beef. Thankfully, It was realized before we served the guests who do not consume the same. still made for a very uncomfortable environment.
Raised a grievence through through the app, and they connected us on a conference call. the person from the hotel decided to hang up mid conversation. A very sad response.
Pls check on what you send to your customers pls!

Mallu Republic is my go-to spot at Talegao for an authentic Malabar breakfast or a quick Swiggy lunch. Their appam and Kerala parotta are my absolute favorites, always soft and perfectly made. I can't resist most of the food, the rich flavors of curry leaves in their tawa fry bangad Or the Kerala chicken fry, absolutely yummy!  Their biryani is also a standout! Every dish brings the taste of Kerala right to my table, making it a must-try for anyone craving genuine, flavorful Malabar cuisine. When at Malli Republic don't forget to try the lemon tea!

description:
**Mallu Republic: A Taste of Kerala in Taleigao**

Nestled in the vibrant community of Taleigao, Mallu Republic has captured the hearts of local food enthusiasts with its commendable rating of 4.2 stars out of 5, backed by a robust 1,241 reviews. This eatery has become synonymous with authentic Malabar flavors, particularly celebrated for its **appams** (31 mentions), **thalis** (17), and **beef fry** (16). As you step inside, the essence of Kerala is palpable, hinting at the culinary journey awaiting you.

**Ambiance & Design**

Mallu Republic exudes a warm and inviting atmosphere, ideal for both casual diners and families. The décor reflects a clever blend of traditional and modern aesthetics, with earthy tones and wooden accents that echo the rich culture of Kerala. From the photos shared by guests, one can appreciate the delightful simplicity of the seating arrangements that create a cozy dining experience. The lighting is soft but sufficient, enhancing the dining atmosphere without overwhelming it. Patrons have noted that the background music contributes to the relaxed vibe, making it a suitable spot for both breakfast and winding down after a long day.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Mallu Republic stands out for its focus on authentic dishes, with **appam** and **Kerala parotta** frequently lauded as must-tries. The food presentation matches its flavor, with vibrant colors and fresh ingredients taking center stage. Diners have raved about the **tawa fry bangad**, complemented by the robust spice blends characteristic of the region. Notably, the **beef fry** and accompanying **beef masala** have garnered positive feedback, proving that meat lovers will leave satisfied. The standout dish, as one reviewer suggests, is the biryani, crafted with care and bursting with rich flavors. Although there have been comments regarding limited vegetarian options, the richness of the non-vegetarian dishes more than compensates.

**Customer Experience & Service**

While Mallu Republic delights many with its culinary offerings, customer service has seen mixed reviews. Some guests reported issues with their orders placed through delivery apps, indicating potential discrepancies in service. However, many patrons appreciate the friendly demeanor of the staff, adding to the warmth of the experience. Although one customer voiced disappointment regarding handling grievances, overall, service appears to be efficient during peak dining hours. Reservations are not mentioned specifically, yet the availability of seating suggests that walk-ins are welcome.

**Popularity & Reviews**

With its growing popularity, Mallu Republic has become a go-to destination for locals craving authentic Malabari cuisine. The buzz on social media underscores its status as a beloved dining spot, with many sharing their experiences alongside appetizing visuals. Critics and casual diners alike agree that a visit here is essential for anyone yearning for the flavors of Kerala, evidenced by the number of positive reviews.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The images captured by customers serve to enhance the narrative of the dining experience at Mallu Republic. The photos depict the delicately crafted **appams**, with their fluffy texture and golden edges, nestled next to vibrant curries—a feast for the eyes as much as for the palate. Other visual highlights showcase the inviting atmosphere of the restaurant, reinforcing its reputation as a comforting retreat for lovers of Kerala cuisine.

In conclusion, Mallu Republic stands as a cherished establishment in Taleigao, where the spices of Kerala meet a welcoming environment. Whether you are a fan of **beef** preparations or simply cannot resist a good **appam**, this restaurant invites you to experience the authentic taste of the Malabar region.
